query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 5 AND q1.favorite_count <= 5000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('android',
'android-layout',
'angular',
'c',
'css3',
'html',
'html5',
'jquery',
'node.js',
'reactjs',
'twitter-bootstrap')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Cleanup',
'Fanatic',
'Great Answer',
'Guru',
'Inquisitive',
'Populist',
'Promoter',
'Proofreader',
'Quorum',
'Vox Populi')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
